      "¹ Children are considered to have received HepB (birth dose) if it was recorded on their card or reported by their mother, regardless of timing.",
      "² BCG, three doses of DPT-containing vaccine, three doses of Polio vaccine given as OPV or IPV, and one dose of measles or MMR",
      "³ BCG, HepB (birth dose), three doses of DPT-containing vaccine, three doses of OPV, two doses of IPV, three doses of PCV, and one dose of MMR",
